        "evidence": "<p>Probability of having T2DM (HgbA1c ≥7.0%) =</p> <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1 / (1 + <em>e</em><sup>-(α + β<sub>1</sub>x<sub>1</sub> + β<sub>2</sub>x<sub>2&nbsp;</sub>+ β<sub>3</sub>x<sub>3&nbsp;</sub>+...+ β<sub>n</sub>x<sub>n</sub>)</sup>&nbsp;)</p> <p>Where:</p> <p>α = -6.322, and additional constants and variables are as follows:</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <table> <tbody> <tr> <td rowspan=\"2\">&nbsp;</td> <td rowspan=\"2\"> <p><strong>β</strong></p> </td> <td colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"2\"> <p><strong>x</strong></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td>&nbsp;</td> <td colspan=\"2\">&nbsp;</td> </tr> <tr> <td> <p>1. Gender</p> </td> <td> <p>-0.879</p> </td> <td colspan=\"2\"> <p>0 if Male</p> <p>1 if Female</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <p>2. Prescribed antihypertensive medication</p> </td> <td>&nbsp;1.222</td> <td colspan=\"2\">&nbsp; <p>0 if No</p> <p>1 if Yes</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <p>3. Prescribed steroids </p> </td> <td> <p>2.191</p> </td> <td colspan=\"2\"> <p>0 if No</p> <p>1 if Yes</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <p>4. Age</p> </td> <td> <p>0.063</p> </td> <td colspan=\"2\"> <p>Age in years</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <p>5. BMI, kg/m<sup>2</sup></p> </td> <td colspan=\"3\"> <p>β<sub>5</sub>x<sub>5</sub>= 0 if &lt;25</p> <p>β<sub>5</sub>x<sub>5</sub>= 0.699 if ≥25 and &lt;27.5</p> <p>β<sub>5</sub>x<sub>5</sub>= 1.97 if ≥27.5 and &lt;30</p> <p>β<sub>5</sub>x<sub>5</sub>= 2.518 if ≥30</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <p>6. Family history</p> </td> <td colspan=\"3\"> <p>β<sub>6</sub>x<sub>6 </sub>= 0 if no diabetic 1st-degree relative</p> <p>β<sub>6</sub>x<sub>6</sub>&nbsp;= 0.728 if parent <em>or</em> sibling with diabetes</p> <p>β<sub>6</sub>x<sub>6</sub> = 0.753 if parent <em>and</em> sibling with diabetes</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <p>7. Smoking history</p> </td> <td colspan=\"3\"> <p>β<sub>7</sub>x<sub>7</sub> = 0 if non-smoker</p> <p>β<sub>7</sub>x<sub>7</sub>&nbsp;= -0.218 if ex-smoker</p> <p>β<sub>7</sub>x<sub>7</sub> = 0.855 if current smoker</p> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table>",
        "facts": "<p>Interpretation:</p> <table> <tbody> <tr> <td> <p><strong>Griffin score cutoff</strong></p> </td> <td> <p><strong>Sensitivity</strong></p> </td> <td> <p><strong>Specificity</strong></p> </td> <td> <p><strong>Positive predictive value</strong></p> </td> <td> <p><strong>Negative predictive value</strong></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <p>0.11</p> </td> <td> <p>85%</p> </td> <td> <p>51%</p> </td> <td> <p>2.2%</p> </td> <td> <p>99.6%</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <p>0.15</p> </td> <td> <p>72%</p> </td> <td> <p>60%</p> </td> <td> <p>2.2%</p> </td> <td> <p>99.4%</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <p>0.17</p> </td> <td> <p>70%</p> </td> <td> <p>64%</p> </td> <td> <p>2.4%</p> </td> <td> <p>99.4%</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <p>0.23</p> </td> <td> <p>63%</p> </td> <td> <p>72%</p> </td> <td> <p>2.8%</p> </td> <td> <p>99.4%</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <p>0.29</p> </td> <td> <p>51%</p> </td> <td> <p>78%</p> </td> <td> <p>2.9%</p> </td> <td> <p>99.2%</p> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table>",
