        "logic": "var calc_output = [];\n\n//user inputs\nvar bx1 = parseFloat(gender);\nvar bx2 = parseFloat(anti);\nvar bx3 = parseFloat(steroids);\nvar bx4 = parseFloat(age) * 0.063;\nvar bx5 = parseFloat(bmi);\nvar bx6 = parseFloat(hx);\nvar bx7 = parseFloat(smoker);\n\nif (bx7 == 0.218) {\n\tbx7 = -0.218\n}\n\n//formula\nvar denominator = 1 + Math.exp(-(-6.322 + bx1 + bx2 + bx3 + bx4 + bx5 + bx6 + bx7));\n\nvar result = 100*(1 / denominator);\n\n//interpretation\nvar i = 'Risk score >11% is 85% sensitive for predicting previously undiagnosed hyperglycemia (HbA1c >= 7.0%)'\nvar j = 'Risk Score <11%';\nif(result > 11){\n\tj = 'Risk Score >11%';\n}\n\n//results\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'mini',\n    value: result.toFixed(1),\n    value_text: '%',\n    message: 'Probability of T2DM'\n});\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'Result',\n    value: (result).toFixed(1),\n    value_text: '%',\n    message: 'Probability of T2DM in previously undiagnosed patient<br/><br/>Risk scores >11% are 85% sensitive for identifying diabetes (HgbA1c ≥7.0%)'\n});",
